text: Terebra nadinae is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Terebridae, the auger snails. The status of this species is uncertain. ==Description== ==Distribution== ==References== * Aubry U. 2008. Nuove terebre dall'Angola. title: Terebra nadinae
